<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 03:18:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国批准摩根士丹利设立本土期货业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-gives-morgan-stanley-approval-launch-local-futures-unit-2024-11-05/</link><description>摩根士丹利已获得最终批准，通过新成立的子公司在中国开展期货业务，成为美国第二大进入世界第二大经济体衍生品市场的公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 02:54:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-gives-morgan-stanley-approval-launch-local-futures-unit-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示，随着形势改善，中国服务业活动有所回升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-picks-up-conditions-improve-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-11-05/</link><description>周二的一项私营部门调查显示，早期迹象表明北京的大规模刺激措施正在帮助改善商业环境，中国10月份的服务业活动以三个月来最快的速度扩张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 01:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-picks-up-conditions-improve-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普警告称，如果当选，他将就芬太尼对墨西哥和中国征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-will-put-tariff-mexico-stop-flow-fentanyl-into-us-2024-11-05/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普周一警告称，如果当选，他将以关税惩罚墨西哥和中国，除非两国政府采取行动阻止芬太尼流入美国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 01:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-will-put-tariff-mexico-stop-flow-fentanyl-into-us-2024-11-05/</guid></item><item><title>高管表示，中国公司看好古巴太阳能发电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-company-bullish-cuban-solar-drive-executive-says-2024-11-04/</link><description>向古巴销售太阳能技术的杭州多佳科技公司称，古巴大力发展太阳能发电的计划对两国来说是双赢，并大力宣传中国的制造业实力和古巴阳光明媚的气候。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 22:43:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-company-bullish-cuban-solar-drive-executive-says-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>Shein 的欧洲实体报告 2023 年销售额增长 68%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-european-entity-reports-68-sales-growth-2023-2024-11-04/</link><description>根据周一公布的年度业绩，Shein 旗下在爱尔兰注册的实体 Infinite Styles Ecommerce Co 的销售额在 2023 年增长了 68%，达到 76.84 亿欧元（83.6 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:23:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-european-entity-reports-68-sales-growth-2023-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国指责俄罗斯和中国在联合国保护朝鲜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-china-shamelessly-protects-emboldens-north-korea-2024-11-04/</link><description>美国周一在联合国安理会谴责俄罗斯和中国“无耻地保护”朝鲜，并鼓励朝鲜进一步违反联合国制裁，平壤承诺加速建设其“核力量”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 17:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-china-shamelessly-protects-emboldens-north-korea-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>英国立法者可能会在明年初就工人权利问题向谢因提出质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-could-question-shein-over-workers-rights-early-next-year-2024-11-04/</link><description>据议会委员会负责人称，英国立法者最早可能在一月份在伦敦上市之前就工人权利问题向在线快时尚集团 Shein 的高管提出质询。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:31:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-could-question-shein-over-workers-rights-early-next-year-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟官员表示，中国电动汽车价格协议需要与关税一样有效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-price-deal-needs-be-effective-tariffs-says-eu-official-2024-11-04/</link><description>这位可能未来的欧盟贸易负责人周一表示，与中国生产商就电动汽车最低价格达成的任何协议都需要像欧盟上周征收的关税一样有效和可执行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-price-deal-needs-be-effective-tariffs-says-eu-official-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国国内旅游需求低迷，万豪下调2024年盈利预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-lowers-2024-profit-forecast-us-china-domestic-tourism-drags-2024-11-04/</link><description>由于中国国内旅游疲软盖过了强劲的团体和国际需求，万豪国际集团周一下调了年度利润预期，导致其股价在早盘交易中下跌 2%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 12:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-lowers-2024-profit-forecast-us-china-domestic-tourism-drags-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国石化与TotalEnergies签署为期15年的液化天然气交易协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-sinopec-signs-agreement-15-yr-lng-deal-with-totalenergies-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气巨头中石化周一表示，已签署协议，从 2028 年开始，为期 15 年，每年从 TotalEnergies 购买 200 万吨液化天然气。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-sinopec-signs-agreement-15-yr-lng-deal-with-totalenergies-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>商务部表示，中国将就欧盟电动汽车最终裁决向世贸组织提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-file-lawsuit-with-wto-against-eus-final-ev-ruling-commerce-ministry-says-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，决定就欧盟对中国产电动汽车的最终反补贴措施向世贸组织提起诉讼。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-file-lawsuit-with-wto-against-eus-final-ev-ruling-commerce-ministry-says-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉 10 月份中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 5.3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-oct-china-made-ev-sales-fall-53-yy-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周一的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉10月份销售了68,280辆中国制造的电动汽车，同比下降5.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 09:36:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-oct-china-made-ev-sales-fall-53-yy-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，马来西亚向越南抱怨南海珊瑚礁扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-complains-vietnam-over-south-china-sea-reef-expansion-sources-say-2024-11-04/</link><description>两名官员告诉路透社，马来西亚已就越南涉嫌扩张南海珊瑚礁向越南发出投诉信，两国均声称拥有该珊瑚礁，这是罕见的不涉及中国的双边升级。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:53:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-complains-vietnam-over-south-china-sea-reef-expansion-sources-say-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车10月销量同比增长3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-october-sales-rise-3-year-on-year-2024-11-04/</link><description>总部位于瑞典的汽车制造商沃尔沃汽车周一表示，10 月份沃尔沃汽车销量同比增长 3%，达到 61,686 辆，主要得益于全电动和插电式混合动力车型在欧洲销量的增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-october-sales-rise-3-year-on-year-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>法国家庭因涉嫌未能删除有害内容而起诉 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/french-families-sue-tiktok-over-alleged-failure-remove-harmful-content-2024-11-04/</link><description>七个法国家庭的律师周一表示，他们对社交媒体巨头 TikTok 提起诉讼，指控该平台让他们的青春期孩子接触有害内容，导致其中两人在 15 岁时自杀。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 07:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/french-families-sue-tiktok-over-alleged-failure-remove-harmful-content-2024-11-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>